    <dashboard name='Story 1' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Vendor Sales &amp; Inventory Performance Analysis</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='198' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='1564' maxwidth='1016' minheight='1564' minwidth='1016' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98976' id='8' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='512'>
            <zone h='2366' id='9' type-v2='title' w='98426' x='787' y='512'>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='96610' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='2878'>
              <zone h='6458' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98426' x='787' y='2878' />
              <zone h='90152' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98426' x='787' y='9336'>
                <flipboard active-id='4' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                  <story-points>
                    <story-point caption='Vendor Sales &amp; Inventory Performance Dashboard' captured-sheet='' id='1' />
                    <story-point caption='Exploratory data Analysis insights' captured-sheet='screenshots1' id='2' />
                    <story-point caption='Correlation insights' captured-sheet='Dashboard 3' id='3' />
                    <story-point caption='Research Questions &amp; Key Findings ' captured-sheet='' id='4' />
                  </story-points>
                </flipboard>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='19693' hidden='true' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='97343' x='2362' y='8951'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='16'>Buisness Problem</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Effective inventory and sales management are critical for optimizing profitability in the retail and wholesale industry. Companies need to ensure that they are not incurring losses due to inefficient pricing, poor inventory turnover, or vendor dependency.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The goal of this analysis is to: </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>● Identify underperforming brands that require promotional or pricing adjustments. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>● Determine top vendors contributing to sales and gross profit. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>● Analyze the impact of bulk purchasing on unit costs. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>● Assess inventory turnover to reduce holding costs and improve efficiency. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>● Investigate the profitability variance between high-performing and low-performing vendors.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3069' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='19390' x='8366' y='8760'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='16'>summary statistics</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='31626' hidden='true' id='12' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='98425' x='1378' y='68648'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Negative &amp; Zero Values:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Gross Profit:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Minimum of -52,002.78, indicating potential losses due to high costs or heavy discounts. This could be due to selling products at lower prices than their purchase costs. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Profit Margin: </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Has a minimum of -∞, which suggests instances where revenue is zero or even lower than the total cost, leading to extreme negative profit margins. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Total Sales Quantity &amp; Sales Dollars:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Some products show zero sales, indicating they were purchased but never sold. These may be slow-moving or obsolete stock, leading to inventory inefficiencies.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Outliers Detected by High Standard Deviations:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Purchase &amp; Actual Prices: </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The maximum values (5,681.81 &amp; 7,499.99) are significantly higher than the mean (24.39 &amp; 35.64), indicating premium product offerings.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Freight Cost:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Extreme variation from 0.09 to 257,032.07 suggests logistics inefficiencies, bulk shipments, or erratic shipping costs across different products.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Stock Turnover: </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Ranges from 0 to 274.5, suggesting some products sell rapidly while others remain unsold for long periods. A value greater than 1 indicates that sales for a product exceed the purchased quantity due to older stock fulfilling orders.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='1918' hidden='true' id='13' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='19980' x='6398' y='9847'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='16'>Correlation Insights</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='18926' hidden='true' id='14' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='96654' x='3642' y='46611'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Purchase Price vs. Total Sales Dollars &amp; Gross Profit:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Weak correlation (-0.012 and -0.016), indicating that price variations do not significantly impact sales revenue or profit</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Total Purchase Quantity vs. Total Sales Quantity</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Strong correlation (0.999), confirming efficient inventory turnover.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Profit Margin vs. Total Sales Price: </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Negative correlation (-0.179), suggesting increasing sales prices may lead to reduced margins, possibly due to competitive pricing pressures.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Stock Turnover vs. Gross Profit &amp; Profit Margin: </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Weak negative correlation (-0.038 &amp; -0.055), indicating that faster stock turnover does not necessarily equate to higher profitability.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='1918' id='15' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='32185' x='2953' y='9910'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Research Questions &amp; Key Findings </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{56E8CDE4-F2AE-4A53-894C-13AA5282641F}' />
    </dashboard>
